Settings
--------

-- \pdfoptionpdfminorversion=4
-- \geometry{paper=a4paper,head=15pt,%
	left=4cm,right=3cm,vmargin=3cm,marginparwidth=3cm}
-- \reversemarginpar
-- \onehalfspacing
-- \sectionmark{\markright{\thesection. #1}}
-- \lhead{\rightmark}\chead{}\rhead{}
-- \lfoot{}\cfoot{}\rfoot{\thepage}
-- \bibsep0pt\bibfont{small}\bibnamestyle{scshape}
-- \graphicspath{figs/}{images/}}
-- \captionsetup{font=small}
-- \tocdepth=4

Naming convention
-----------------

the author, we	:= me
the team	:= all the monkeys (including me)
the reader	:= you
you		:= general subject
caller		:= user or function
receiver	:= `this'

Comment conventions
-------------------

{text}		"text" is a \Keyword
[text]		"text" is a \Target
<text>		"text" is a \Topic
/text/		undecided

